These adidas shoes are designed in collaboration with Marvel, with a striking color palette inspired by Miles Morales's suit. Each pair is individually numbered, so if you're lucky enough to secure a pair, rest assured they're one of a kind. The mid-cut upper feels soft and comfortable, and the 4D latticed midsole transforms impact forces into forward motion to take you effortlessly from one place to another. The reflective print on the toecap is a nod to Miles’s Evolved Venom Super Power.
